Package au.csiro.pathling.library.query

Class QueryBuilder<T extends QueryBuilder<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.csiro.pathling.library.query.QueryBuilder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - actual type of the query
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AggregateQuery, ExtractQuery
    public abstract class QueryBuilder<T extends QueryBuilder<?>>
extends Object
    Base class for queries that use filters. Subclasses must implement the execute() method to perform the actual execution of the query.
